import React, { Component } from "react"
import {BrowserRouter, Routes, Route} from "react-router-dom"
import Profiles from "./components/Profiles/Profiles"
import AddProfileForm from "./components/FormAddProfiles/AddProfileForm"
import Repo from "./components/Repo/Repo"
import UpdateProfile from "./components/UpdateProfile/UpdateProfile"
import AdminPanel from "./views/AdminPanel"
import PublicView from "./views/PublicView"
import Login from "./views/Login"
import Aboutus from "./components/Aboutus/Aboutus"

class Rotas extends Component {

    render(){
        return(
            <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
              <Route exact path="/"  element={<PublicView/>} />
              <Route exact path="/nos" element={<Aboutus />} />
              <Route exact path="/login" element={<Login/>} />
              <Route exact path="/admin" element={<AdminPanel/>} />
              <Route exact path="/admin/profiles" element={<Profiles/>} />
              <Route exact path="/admin/create" element={<AddProfileForm />} />
              <Route exact path="/admin/update" element={<UpdateProfile />} />
              <Route exact path="/admin/repo" element={<Repo />} />
            </Routes>
            </BrowserRouter>
        )
    }
  }
  
  export default Rotas
